I was also thinking and couldn't come up with an answer. (maybe someone can) Since McQuaid left, can you think of any class ability nerfs pertaining to casters? <br>
Some items sure, but anything along the lines of reduced damage on dots, mobs with unalterable movement rates, unstunnable/unmezzable?<br>
<br>
